The formation of SrSO4 on LSCF is critically dependent on operating temperature. For example, Wang et al. [224] annealed LSCF pellets in 20 ppm SO2 at temperatures ranging from 400 to 900 °C and found that SrSO4 formed on LSCF surfaces at high temperatures ⩾\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
